snippet.title: Labyrneath II Walkthrough
snippet.description:
This is a walkthrough of the game "Labyrneath II".

Play the game here: https://www.newgrounds.com/portal/view/729120

You can visit my Patreon page if you want or something:
https://www.patreon.com/awalkthroughlife

Game created by 44Magdalene (Matthew Morgan):
Music credits:
Jarico:
https://soundcloud.com/jaricomusic
https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=100012860439675
https://www.instagram.com/jaricomusiccc
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC8hwz1M-bL8DFUqS1SdA7vw

Still Back by ZAYFALL https://soundcloud.com/zayfallmusic
Creative Commons — Attribution 3.0 Unported  — CC BY 3.0 
https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/3.0/
Free Download / Stream: http://bit.ly/2QJ2XY0 
Music promoted by Audio Library https://youtu.be/bkRr409ghOQ

Cloudy by KODOMOi
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tZeD0G5XW10

Music provided by RFM: https://youtu.be/_5RShlsL5xo
_________
Game description:
It's one thing to find the Fountain of Youth--it's another to get out with any of it. Navigate 15 new levels of traps, obstacles, and enemies on your way out of the jungle.

AWSD or arrow keys to move. Spacebar also doubles as a jump button, and the game supports a controller in everything but menus. P, M, or Enter to pause.
_________
#labyrneath #walkthrough
